--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DESCRIPTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This role manages pciutils.

The pciutils package contains various utilities for inspecting and setting
devices connected to the PCI bus. The utilities provided require kernel version
2.1.82 or newer (which support the /proc/bus/pci interface).

For more detailed information on the usage and available configuration options
please consult the following sections.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
USAGE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALL
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: pciutils
       pciutils_state: 'install'

REMOVE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: pciutils
       pciutils_state: 'remove'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VARIABLES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ROLE
  pciutils_state
    Specify predetermined 'pciutils_state' variable (string).

    Install: 'true' | 'yes' | 'install'
    Remove : 'false' | 'no' | 'remove'
    Default: 'install'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DEPENDENCIES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

PACKAGES
  pciutils: >= 3.1
    RedHat, CentOS, Gentoo

ROLES

VARIABLES

